                  </h3>
                  <ol class="space-y-2 text-gray-700">
                    <li class="flex items-start">
                      <span class="bg-green-100 text-green-800 text-xs font-medium px-2 py-1 rounded-full mr-3 mt-0.5">1</span>
                      Take the M56 westbound towards Chester
                    </li>
                    <li class="flex items-start">
                      <span class="bg-green-100 text-green-800 text-xs font-medium px-2 py-1 rounded-full mr-3 mt-0.5">2</span>
                      Exit at Junction 12 for the A557 towards Runcorn
                    </li>
                    <li class="flex items-start">
                      <span class="bg-green-100 text-green-800 text-xs font-medium px-2 py-1 rounded-full mr-3 mt-0.5">3</span>
