                </svg>
              </div>
              <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-800">By Bus</h3>
            </div>
            <div class="space-y-3 text-gray-700">
              <p><strong>Local Services:</strong> Arriva North West operates local routes</p>
              <p><strong>From Chester:</strong> Bus route 84 (check current timetables)</p>
              <p><strong>From Northwich:</strong> Local connecting services available</p>
              <p><strong>Walking Distance:</strong> 10-15 minutes from nearest bus stop</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="mt-8 text-center">
          <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4">Need help planning your journey?</p>
          <a href="tel:01606889455" class="inline-flex items-center bg-green-600 text-white px-6 py-3 rounded-lg font-semibold hover:bg-green-700 transition-colors">
            <svg class="w-5 h-5 mr-2" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M3 5a2 2 0 012-2h3.28a1 1 0 01.948.684l1.498 4.493a1 1 0 01-.502 1.21l-2.257 1.13a11.042 11.042 0 005.516 5.516l1.13-2.257a1 1 0 011.21-.502l4.493 1.498a1 1 0 01.684.949V19a2 2 0 01-2 2h-1C9.716 21 3 14.284 3 6V5z"></path>
